      "description": {
        "en": "FOR YOU REAL ESTATE is proud to present this brand new 1-bedroom apartment, offering the best layout in the building with abundant storage, a park view, and immediate move-in readiness.\n\nProperty Highlights:\n- Fully Furnished and Equipped with appliances\n- Brand New Unit – never lived in\n- Vacant and Ready to Move In\n- Best Layout in the Building – thoughtfully designed\n- Plenty of Storage Space – a rare feature in Dubai\n\nBuilding Amenities:\n- 2 Swimming Pools (including ladies-only pool)\n- Fully Equipped Gym\n- Landscaped Gardens and Park Access\n- Children's Play Area\n- Covered Parking\n- Advanced Security System and 24/7 Security\n\nIn FOR YOU REAL ESTATE\nWe provide comprehensive real estate services tailored to your needs.\nAdvantages of working with us:\nDetailed market analysis – we select the perfect property based on your request\nWe manage the entire transaction process from purchase to sale\nAccess to exclusive listings and the best options\nFirst class service. We are always for long-term cooperation\nOur team has the best brokers\nWe have been working in the market with premium clients for a long time\nFor You Real Estate L.L.C. is based in The Onyx Tower 2, office 910 with a team of agents who are focused on the sales, rentals and management of properties in Dubai."
