      "description": {
        "en": "Offered on behalf of For You Real Estate, a modern 1.5-bedroom unit with a balcony in the prestigious Sobha Crest Grande.\n\n• 1.5 Bedrooms\n• 2 Bathroom\n• Spacious Unit\n• Balcony with views of Hartland and Ras Al Khor\n• Floor: 3\n• Parking Space\n\nFacilities and Amenities:\n\n• Swimming pools\n• BBQ area\n• Lagoon\n• Gym\n• Sauna\n• Steam room\n\nSobha Crest Grande is a high-end residential project that offers a luxurious living experience with top-notch facilities. An off-plan project with handover scheduled for Q4 2025.\n\n• 50% of the payment plan is paid\n• Payment plan until the end of 2025\n\nAbout For You Real Estate - we are a full-service real estate agency with a quality approach to every client. We are ready to help with every stage of the transaction, from the very beginning and registration to the turnkey delivery of your apartment in short-term rentals."
      },
