      "description": {
        "en": "Gemz is a 14-storey premium pyramid-shaped building in the Al Furjan area. The complex will have 270 apartments, some of them with private swimming pools. The Gemz residential complex is located next to a major transport intersection.\n\n- 5–7 minutes by car (the station belongs to the longest red line, which was the first to appear in the city)\n- 30 min Dubai International Airport (DXB)\n- 22 min area of the World Expo 2020\n- 10 min Ibn Battuta Mall\n- 15 min The Walk embankment 7 km long with views of skyscrapers and\nyachts\n\nWithin a radius of 1 km from the complex there is a school with a British curriculum, The Arbor School.\n\nIn the Gemz complex, residents will enjoy hotel-level services:\n- public pool and personal pools on terraces\n- sauna\n- your own gym\n- yoga zone\n- tennis court and cricket field\n- lobby with waiting area and coworking space\n- banquet hall\n- beauty salons\n- garden on site\n- playgrounds for children\n- barbecue area\n- outdoor cinema\n- rooftop observation deck\n- green terraces at roof level\n\nFOR YOU REAL ESTATE is dedicated to delivering our clients a wide array of services: sales, rentals, property management, consulting services, mortgage brokerage, and many more."
      },
